{"tid":1799004,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"問馬雲借錢的窮L - 陳也","createTime":"2019-12-26T15:36:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T15:37:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"74b174f9ddae83849119eb7ca814dbe1336031f7","tid":1799004,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T15:36:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20191226/20831554/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191226%2F20831554%2F&d=TEMpI0ru4fZij%2BnpPgfFHXWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=8be8a7db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191226%2F20831554%2F&h=f0b0987c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20191226/20831554/</a><br />\n<br />\n問馬雲借錢的窮L - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191226/large/1577257600_2bfb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191226%2Flarge%2F1577257600_2bfb.jpg&h=25724db8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n歐新社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n馬雲公開講，一日之內連接五個電話，朋友問佢借錢，云云。邊五個？估吓先。<br />\n<br />\n林兆波都算朋友，左手㩒實右手，擺明極度手緊，着草肯定冇得慳。以林兄身份，逃到天涯海角才能避開甴總的追捕，雖然叻唔過轉數快的馬老闆，波兄還是求救：我唔想去首都食餃子！<br />\n<br />\n民&times;聯養起大批落選的兄弟，打算叫他們趁無警時份，打劫金鋪幫補吓。但金鋪只係一百萬上落，唔夠洗腳，所以主席急call馬老師，借住先。<br />\n<br />\n何滾妖自毀山墳得個桔，馬都冇得跑，欠落有PK721照住的元朗白衫那條尾數，已經利疊利到火星人才還得到。問世間，唔問馬雲借，唔通問米咩。<br />\n<br />\n邱局長唔識分藍黃，打畀紅到發紫的馬雲，是正確決定。不過馬雲喂了柒聲，罵一句黐&times;線，收線。<br />\n<br />\n無面可露的689打通電話，馬雲一直跟他講雞腸，在腸與腸中間終於搵到機會開口借。最衰都係懸紅N個百萬，福建汕頭乜春社團篤完灰狂追佢尾數。如果唔畀，淋紅油等佢日日做聖誕老人咁話。戥佢陰功lol。 <br />\n<br />\n陳也<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"5e6fc5b6dce22f82c54d5735d0f686974ee5faf6","tid":1799004,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T15:37:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">無忘承諾 並肩同行<br />\n民陣元誕大遊行</span><br />\n日期 : 1月1日 (三)<br />\n時間：14:00<br />\n地點：維園中央草坪 ==&gt; 遮打道行人專用區"}]}